# matrix-copy-message-bot

## Install

```
git clone git@github.com:alx/matrix-copy-message-bot.git
cd matrix-copy-message-bot
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip3 install -r requirements.txt
cp config.json.sample config.json
python3 app.py
```

## Usage

- Go to MATRIX_CONTROL_CHATROOM_ID chatroom
- Post a message and react to it with :cowboy_hat_face: emoji
- Message will be copied to SIGNAL_DESTINATION_GROUP_ID and MATRIX_DESTINATION_CHATROOM_ID

